                <title type="Complete" ref="LIT2358Sirach" xml:lang="gez">ትምህርተ፡ ትበብ፡ ወቃለ፡
                  ተግሣጽ፡ ጸሐፍኩ፡ ውስተ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ አነ፡ <persName ref="PRS5685Jesusth">ኢያሱ፡ ሲራክ፡ ወልደ፡ ሲራክ፡ ወልደ፡ አልዓዛር፡</persName> ዘኢየሩሳሌም።</title>
                <textLang mainLang="gez" />
                <note>The division is the same as in the Greek text.</note>
                <note>The text belongs to the same recension as <ref type="mss" corresp="BNFet6#ms_i7"/> and <ref type="mss" corresp="BNFet8#ms_i5"/>. It agrees the most with 
                  <ref type="mss" corresp="BNFet6#ms_i7"/>.</note>
